{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, OpenPose, HMR, OpenNI, VoxelNet, PoseNet, etc.",
    "as discussed in the works of literature are the most popular pose estimation algorithms and are being adopted by many researchers.",
    "Apart from these state-of-the-art algorithms, the MediaPipe framework also yields minimum error and perfectly classifies the various joint landmarks.",
    "As per the authors' knowledge, the real-time positioning of a humanoid robot arm using the MediaPipe framework is not reported.",
    "Also, the performance of the MediaPipe pose estimation framework in terms of the standard error is missing."
  ]
}